metadata.name: The Green Confusion
metadata.description:
" The Green Confusion " is an artistic collage based on one of the paintings by  " Hubert Robert "   in neo-rococo style besides some parts of some photos by  " Elliott Erwitt "  , " Jacques Henri Lartigue " , " Robert Capa "  and other artists . 
The main purpose of this collage was to transfer some B&W characters from photographer's works into a magnificent part of  heaven to destroy the eternal joy of its silence . 
 ENJOY .
